## ğŸ¯ Objectives
The visualization aims to answer key global questions:

- How have COâ‚‚ emissions evolved as countries developed economically?
- Do richer nations emit more or less COâ‚‚ per capita?
- How does an aging population relate to economic and environmental trends?
- Which countries show strong sustainability improvements?
- How do developing vs developed regions compare over time?

